---
description: A cave of different types and seasons
---

cave-type
===
- one of:
    - sea cave, {#underwater}
    - lava cave, {#lava}
    - ice cave, {#ice}
    - crystal cave, {#crystal}

Start
===
cave, cave walls
cavern
- subterranean interior
- 50% +cave-type
- rugged rock walls
- $intensity-word stalagmites
- $intensity-word stalactites
- [i>70%] vast echoing chamber
- [i<25%] cramped narrow passage

; extra depth — admitted at lower focus, stripped as focus rises
[f<65%] {#color} crystal
[f<65%] underground pool
[f<55%] bioluminescent glow
[f<55%] {#color} gemstone
[f<50%] dripping water, damp stone
[f<45%] winding tunnels, mineral veins
[f<35%] carved structures, ancient stone pillars

; out-of-subject fluff — only at low focus
[f<25%] distant settlement, abandoned mine cart
[f<20%] underground waterfall
[f<15%] glimpse of a city beyond the entrance

; atmosphere garnish
[f<70%] {#nature}
[f<60%] {#water}
[f<45%] {#wildlife}
[f<45%] {#eerie}
[f<35%] {#mystical}
[f<70%] {#weather}
